See Who is Online - GP:
select * from DYNAMICS..ACTIVITY
select * from tempdb..DEX_LOCK
select * from tempdb..DEX_SESSION


Get Users and Permissions for Nav/GP:
Select [User].[User Name],[User].[State],[Access Control].[Role ID],[Access Control].[Company Name]
From [User]
INNER JOIN [Access Control]
ON [User].[User Security ID]=[Access Control].[User Security ID]
